text: Mizanur Rahman is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Mymensingh-7. ==Career== Rahman was elected to parliament from Mymensingh-7 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1973. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:1st Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:People from Mymensingh District
title: Mizanur Rahman (politician)
